                       {{${1:number}}}
      ************************************************

      ${2:Insert your Markdown blocks in here ...}

      ************************************************
    """
    'description': """
      You can bundle multiple blocks to one effect block by enclosing them into two lines of stars (*). The rest works exactly as block effects...
